'''Tisent''' ([[Asget]]: '''Tisnin''') d asafar ilan (yesɛan) s talɣa tagejdant [[uddis akruran]] umi qqaren [[Kluṛ n Sudium]] (NaCl) ig kecmen deg tegrawt meqqren n [[tisent (takrura)|tisnin]], Tisent d asafar yellan deg [[agama|ugama]] s talɣa n [[agres|igersen]] (cristal) yettwassen s [[tamment n wulli]] (Halite), Maca tisent tettili s waṭas deg [[aman|waman]] n [[ilel|illan]] acku d tisent tkd asger agejdan n yimɣuzen yellan deg [[ilel|illan]] d [[agraw|igarawen]] s wazal n 35 g/l (oz 1.2) d [[amareɣ|umareɣ]] 3,5%, Tisent d imsefki i tudert n [[afgan|ifganen]] d [[aɣersiw|iɣersiwen]]  acku yettilin deg iẓeṭṭiwen n iɣersiwen ugar n wid n [[imɣi|yemɣan]]

